examples: Someone must have peached on us!
It was the biggest peach pick in years.
We planted a peach tree in the backyard.
Anderton scored a peach of a goal.
He fondly remembers his old Studebaker as being a peach of a car.
Baseball player Ty Cobb was also known by the sobriquet “The Georgia Peach.”
